==========
Operations
==========

Mapping buffers
---------------

All buffers used for data and parameters need to be premapped to the driver
before use.

V4L2 ref: VIDIOC_REQBUF for DMABUF/USERPTR buffers

Queue a command
---------------

Queues a single command to PSYS.

V4L2 ref: VIDIOC_QBUF

Poll for events
---------------

Poll for any events that client has requested.

Dequeue an event
----------------

V4L2 ref: VIDIOC_DQEVENT
